      -#  And if you can offer a recurring monthly donation for as little as $1, we would really
      -#  appreciate, AND - ANYONE SUBSCRIBED TO A MONTHLY DONATION (Graduate or higher) will be
      -#  granted a free account for the first 3 years once Makeabox Premium launches.
